parameters:
Old Farmer: It may seem like an empty place, but this is a
fulfilled place.

Old Farmer: Oh, it's a blessing to meet a priest. I can no
longer move my legs and go to the church.

Old Farmer: The Terios religion is a wonderful thing. To
live without forgetting faith is not the way of an imperial
person.

Old Farmer: I feel like the empire is starting to forget
what truly matters.

Farmer's Wife: My husband is always caught up in
complicated things. Please be someone he can talk to.
